{"tid":2516264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子迷糊醒來發現身處飛鵝山山邊　手腳擦損","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T15:51:32.000Z","uid":212249,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdb5902f033dc03d8bdf9e358b96ee70bf19242","tid":2516264,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210504/466186355953635328205834.jpeg/rwFV1JYs7T4Docue76d7x9HHcdUv3eLSJ2UAUCdlAFA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210504%2F466186355953635328205834.jpeg%2FrwFV1JYs7T4Docue76d7x9HHcdUv3eLSJ2UAUCdlAFA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=52c8300f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨1時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指自己一覺醒來後，竟身處在山邊，而銀包等財物已不知所終，於是報案。由於他不知身處何方，報案中心人員着他尋找一些地標以推測其位置。最終，事主發現附近有一支街燈，遂將燈柱號碼報上。<br />\n<br />\n報案中心人員迅即得知其位置，在黃大仙飛鵝山扎山道一處山邊，於是派警員及通知消防處調派救護車前往現場。救援人員最終尋獲事主，他受了輕傷，由救護車送往觀塘基督教聯合醫院治理，送院時清醒。事主在醫院查明未有失去財物，在妻子陪同下表示毋須警方協助。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事主姓劉，30歲。他手腳擦損，惟對於之前發生何事卻「斷片」。"},{"pid":"7d660ff01853c254fca28107c0f286998097d487","tid":2516264,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d6fd9fdd635359bea1a87fde6bd55839934f17","tid":2516264,"uid":34394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"之前單飛鵝山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddd239df85d9b5c13325d965eb17eb4a9ce03f5","tid":2516264,"uid":129619,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"石樂蕎 2.0"},{"pid":"c4009ceb326dc48e794b46f554da424ca46be1e7","tid":2516264,"uid":68668,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"由結界出返嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca78d54ae1b4b771f3df56757a70fb73daec9